data.description: Explore this spacious two-story gem featuring 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and an inviting office space. The primary bedroom conveniently graces the ground floor, while three additional bedrooms reside on the second floor, accompanied by a versatile loft area perfect for a second family room, home gym, or playroom. The kitchen is a culinary haven with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a charming breakfast bar for additional seating. The primary bedroom's ensuite pampers with a walk-in shower and a separate indulgent soaking tub. Outside, the backyard beckons with a covered patio, promising endless possibilities for relaxation and entertainment. Come and discover all that this wonderful home has to offer!
